### 1. HTTP/REST Module (CRUD)

### Lấy danh sách Users
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users?page=1&limit=10

### Tạo User (POST)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alex",
  "email": "alex@example.com"
}

### Cập nhật toàn bộ (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/v1/users/ID_CUA_USER_O_TREN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alex Updated",
  "email": "alex_updated@example.com"
}

### 2. Streaming (SSE)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/streaming/sse

### 3. Long Polling (Mở tab 1)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/streaming/long-polling/12345

### 3. Long Polling Trigger (Mở tab 2)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/streaming/long-polling/12345/trigger
Content-Type: text/plain

Data ready!
